tv.amwa.maj.model.impl

Interface DefinitionType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassDefinitionImpl, CodecDefinitionImpl, ContainerDefinitionImpl, DataDefinitionImpl, DefinitionObjectImpl, InterpolationDefinitionImpl, KLVDataDefinitionImpl, MetaDefinitionImpl, OperationDefinitionImpl, ParameterDefinitionImpl, PluginDefinitionImpl, PropertyDefinitionImpl, PropertyWrapperDefinitionImpl, SingletonTypeDefinitionImpl, TaggedValueDefinitionImpl, TypeDefinitionCharacterImpl, TypeDefinitionEnumerationImpl, TypeDefinitionExtendibleEnumerationImpl, TypeDefinitionFixedArrayImpl, TypeDefinitionImpl, TypeDefinitionIndirectImpl, TypeDefinitionIntegerImpl, TypeDefinitionObjectReferenceImpl, TypeDefinitionOpaqueImpl, TypeDefinitionRecordImpl, TypeDefinitionRenameImpl, TypeDefinitionSetImpl, TypeDefinitionStreamImpl, TypeDefinitionStringImpl, TypeDefinitionStrongObjectReferenceImpl, TypeDefinitionVariableArrayImpl, TypeDefinitionWeakObjectReferenceImpl

    public interface DefinitionType

    Interface supported by all definition objects and meta definition objects. These kinds of objects are identified by a AUID, have a name and an optional description.
